OL,3,CBahamas PM: Country could be condemed
OL,4,Cto a 'watery grave' over climate crisis
OL,6,FFrom above, The Bahamas look like a
OL,7,Ftropical paradise but the reality on
OL,8,Fthe ground is that they are at risk.
OL,10,F80% of the islands which make up The
OL,11,FBahamas are less than three metres
OL,12,Fabove sea level, making them very
OL,13,Fvulnerable to climate-induced sea
OL,14,Flevel rise.
OL,16,FSevere weather events like hurricanes
OL,17,Fare also becoming more frequent. In
OL,18,F2019, Hurricane Dorian became the most
OL,19,Fintense tropical cyclone to ever hit
OL,20,Fthe islands causing 84 deaths and a
OL,21,Frecord $5.1 billion dollars of damage.
