OL,3,CBahamas PM: Country could be condemed
OL,4,Cto a 'watery grave' over climate crisis
OL,6,F"We have produced the challenges that
OL,7,Fwe face today because of our own
OL,8,Fconduct and our own action.
OL,10,F"There are real issues to be seen if
OL,11,Fyou do not just sit in your ivory
OL,12,Ftower and talk about these issues."
OL,14,FHe is appealing for the world to take
OL,15,Fthe crisis seriously and follow
OL,16,Fdiscussions like the annual COP
OL,17,Fmeetings with meaningful action.
OL,19,F"If not, we will be condemned to a
OL,20,Fwatery grave or become climate
OL,21,Frefugees" he warns.
