OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew is the only journalist on board
OL,8,Fthe British research ship the RRS Sir
OL,9,FDavid Attenborough, as it takes part
OL,10,Fin an expedition deep within the
OL,11,FAntarctic Circle.
OL,13,FNo other British ship has made the
OL,14,Fjourney this far south, this late in
OL,15,Fwinter, since the explorer Sir Ernest
OL,16,FShackleton's ill-fated Endurance
OL,17,Fvoyage, when his ship became trapped
OL,18,Fin the pack ice and sank in 1915.
